  <description><![CDATA[<p>Excellent service and a central village location are just two of the great features of the Pan Pacific Whistler Village Centre. This all-suite accommodation is the perfect home from home in Whistler, just minutes from the slopes.</p>
<h2>Central village location</h2>
<p>A pretty five minute walk from the hotel will take you to the Excalibur Gondola which gives you access to the Blackcomb mountain side of the resort.</p>
<p>Another minute walk will take you to the Whistler Village Gondola which whisks you to the top of Whistler mountain. From either gondola you can explore the whole of North America's largest ski resort.</p>
<p><span>The slope-side valet ski storage makes it easy to get on and off the slopes in no time.</span></p>
<p>The hotel backs onto the Village Stroll, Whistler's main street with a variety of world class restaurants, cosy cafes, boutique shops and lively bars to explore.</p>
<h2>All-suite accommodation</h2>
<p><span>The Pan Pacific Whistler Village Centre's all-suite room types are the perfect home from home. All rooms have full kitchens so you can self cater or head out to the Village Stroll for some fantastic dining options.</span></p>
<p><span>Cosy up by your fireplace or marvel at the stunning snowy landscape from your balcony.</span></p>
<p><span>Every morning you can fuel up for the day with the complimentary </span>hot breakfast buffet with a selection of tea, coffee, fruit juice, <span>cereal, yogurt, pastries, fruit and toast.</span></p>
<h2><span>Craft cocktails in the Raven Room</span></h2>
<p><span>The on-site Raven Room is popular with guests and lovers of good food and drink. Their ever-changing cocktail menu promises something new and unique in every drink while their food focuses on local Pacific flavours.</span></p>
<h2><span>Heated outdoor hot tubs</span></h2>
<p><span>There's nowhere better to relax after a day on the slopes that a bubbling hot tub with views of the snow-capped mountains. The outdoor patio has a saltwater lap pool and two hot tubs to decompress in.</span></p>
<p><span>The hotel also has great on-site spa facilities with massages, facials and treatments bookable locally.</span></p>]]></description>
